On 6/7/03 9:09 AM, "Jasan C." <type2-78(-at-)attbi.com> wrote:

> My guess is that it is most likely L90D/ Pastell White. The type2 library
> has some good lists for all the codes under paint once you find it.

I think L90D Pastell White came later. L282 Lotus White is more likely for
early Campmobiles as they have a greyish look about them.

Find the plate code and look up the color code in this table...

http://www.type2.com/m-codes/t2colors.html

...or look for the silver color code sticker.

